            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Veneri <supplied reason="lost">signum</supplied> <lb n="2"/>cum duabu<supplied reason="lost">s statuis</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Iubae et Ptol<supplied reason="lost">emaei pro</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>batoriis quat<supplied reason="lost">tuor insignibus</supplied> <lb n="5"/>ornatis <expan><abbr>Serg</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Sul<supplied reason="lost">picius<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Vielleicht handelt es sich beim Dedikanten um Serg. Sulpicius Galba. (B): Z. 3/4: [impe]/ratoriis; Z. 5: [or]natis.</p>
            </div>
